headline: The Bull Case For lululemon athletica (LULU) Could Change Following NFL Partnership Announcement With Fanatics
summary: On October 15, 2025, NFL and Fanatics jointly announced a partnership with lululemon athletica to launch NFL team-branded apparel for men and women, marking lululemon's first collaboration with the league and introducing products for all 32 teams. This agreement enables lululemon to access the sports fan merchandise market and potentially expand its reach to new customer segments during a period of challenging domestic demand.
